pulses.name: 20241212 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
12 Dec 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- China (CN) - China is a major source of cyber activities, primarily associated with the Mozi botnet, which has multiple instances of exploitation, including arbitrary file uploads and command injections targeting various devices.
- India (IN) - India shows a high concentration of attacks, particularly involving the Mozi botnet and remote command injection vulnerabilities, indicating an active landscape for cyber exploitation.
- United States (US) - The US features prominently in various cyber threats, including attempts to exploit Apache Shiro vulnerabilities and SSH brute force attempts, reflecting a diverse range of cyber activities originating from this country.

https://www.linkedin.com/posts/starlightintel_cybersecurity-cyberattack-rce-activity-7272980077137539073-jWtL?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop
